民，要學馬丁路德金。<br />\n我不反對不支持勇武，但理解。請在勇武前冷靜想清楚後果(自己和旁人）.<br />\n「我有一個夢」背後有「選票與子彈」支持同保護<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/選票還是子彈\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E9%81%B8%E7%A5%A8%E9%82%84%E6%98%AF%E5%AD%90%E5%BD%88&d=05%2BDYq1PAX1syIB%2FutXPahVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=f26126ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/選票還是子彈</a>"},{"pid":"ca7e84a6ee24b49609721c2b1444ea512abb8769","tid":1314372,"uid":85629,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"af3e056e94e8b6b656a270317c2f9b81977b54f3","tid":1314372,"uid":28831,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T07:35:33.000Z","msg":"佢帶頭暴動先咪投票比佢囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T07:43:29.000Z","msg":"果個係南亞雄將軍"},{"pid":"b7d2bff799b558eb77d789d3b6f86ccfda30084f","tid":1314372,"uid":25781,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T07:43:37.000Z","msg":"掉轉頭講 , 當呢件真心膠都咁講得 , 啫係佢信佢班和理非支持者開始理解勇武嘅必要 , 大家可以放膽 唔駛怕失民心了"},{"pid":"7dbe1f076efcff36a53dee050763572639fc4bd8","tid":1314372,"uid":10141,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T07:44:22.000Z","msg":"蠢女人<br />\n<br />\n見和理非個勢唔對路就痴埋嚟呃選票"},{"pid":"9da9701d05519407f40ff39467d66d978f47c6b8","tid":1314372,"uid":97451,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T07:44:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a4adc2e1f453e87d8428e1c5a3fb21ebfd89bd31","tid":1314372,"uid":140411,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"8bc3ec3a93d2eaf419a240c9f0246f799757656c","tid":1314372,"uid":125168,"like":180,"dislike":1,"score":179,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T06:49:43.000Z","msg":"林鄭下台都無用㗎喇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T07:44:35.000Z","msg":"要成個狗隊解散/團體式問責<br />\n如果唔係 真係唔撚收貨<br />\n警權過大 濫用權力暴力 就算下一個上台都會照用呢套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dcb1b4ca478267d9de7198cfcd4e9ed58490a77","tid":1314372,"uid":270824,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote"